{"article_id":"MxRYXp1nXjbmZtid","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump said Friday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he will beef up existing and planned tariffs on billions of dollars of Chinese goods , in the latest escalation of an increasingly bitter trade war","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that has rattled global markets .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"$ 250 billion worth of Chinese imports","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"being taxed at 25 %","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"instead will face a 30 % levy as of Oct. 1 ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"while a remaining $ 300 billion in goods will be taxed at 15 %","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"- instead of 10 % -","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"when they take effect Sept. 1 .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The president said","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"he was striking back at Beijing ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"which earlier in the day said","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"it planned to impose additional tariffs on key American goods .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"However , it was more of an incremental step","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"than Mr. Trump teased earlier in the day ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"in which he suggested","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"he would try to move American business out of China .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"\" We must Balance this very unfair Trading Relationship , \"","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Trump said on Twitter .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"\" China should not have put new Tariffs on 75 BILLION DOLLARS of United States product","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"( politically motivated ! ) . \"","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"A top Republican , Sen. Charles E. Grassley of Iowa , backed Mr. Trump","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"but warned","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that stiffer tariffs may harm to farmers .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"it ' s up to China , not Mr. Trump , to forge a way out of the standoff .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"\" The only way","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"to end this trade war","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"is for China to come to the table and negotiate seriously on an enforceable deal","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that ends its bad behavior and unfair trade practices .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"In the meantime , tariffs can not be the only negotiating tool .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Tariffs are not a long-term solution , \"","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"said Mr. Grassley , chairman of the Senate Finance Committee .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Yet Rep. T.J. Cox , a Democrat from California ' s Central Valley , said","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"it ' s Mr. Trump who must set the tone .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"\" This administration should immediately end this disastrous policy","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and help get our agriculture economy back on its feet , \"","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"\" It ' s impossible for businesses to plan for the future in this type of environment .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"The administration ' s approach clearly isn ' t working ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"and the answer isn ' t more taxes on American businesses and consumers .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Where does this end ? \"","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"said David French , senior vice president of government relations at the National Retail Federation .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s announcement followed a tumultuous day on Wall Street .","depth":2},{"id":45,"text":"Stocks plummeted","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"after Mr. Trump said on Twitter","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"he would compel U.S. companies to pull out of China ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"citing Beijing ' s new tariffs .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"China said","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"it will impose some of the new tariffs","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"beginning Sept. 1 ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"with others kicking in on Dec. 15 .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"The Dow Jones Industrial Average fell 623 points , or 2.37 % ,","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"to close at 25,628 .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"The tech-heavy Nasdaq lost 3 % ,","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"and the S & P 500 dropped 2.59 % .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"Investors reacted to the series of threatening tweets","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"that Mr. Trump issued at 10:59 a.m .","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"The president \" ordered \" U.S. companies to start moving out of China ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"although legally he has no authority","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"to force such action .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"\" We don ' t need China","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"and , frankly , would be far better off","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"without them .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"The vast amounts of money","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"made and stolen by China from the United States , year after year , for decades ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"will and must STOP , \"","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Trump tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"\" Our great American companies are hereby ordered to immediately start looking for an alternative to China ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"including bringing your companies HOME","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and making your products in the USA , \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"he added .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"he also wants shipping entities such as FedEx , UPS , the U.S . Postal Service and Amazon to \" search for and refuse \" packages","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that contain illicit fentanyl , a powerful synthetic opioid","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"that often comes from China .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"\" President Xi said","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"this would stop","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"- it didn ' t , \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Trump wrote ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"referring to Mr. Xi ' s promise","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"to schedule the drug","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"and crack down on clandestine labs in China .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":167,"left":127,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":105,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":101,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":93,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":86,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":0,"right":85,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":85,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":3,"right":91,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":88,"right":90,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":88,"left":87,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":89,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":96,"right":99,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":10,"right":95,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":11,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":14,"right":98,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":15,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":102,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":116,"right":125,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},